						               													<description>In The Claw, players will play as someone who really likes toys and are competing with each other to get as many favourite toys as possible. Players will use a machine with the shape of a Claw to take the toys and along the way they will become more and more joyful due to the JoyPoints that are attached to their collected toys.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Claw is a game for 2-4 players where players are competing to collect as many JoyPoints as possible. JoyPoint is the value stated on Toy Cards which are spread in the game arena; on Dream Cards that can be collected as set collections after its required conditions are fulfilled; and also on some Trick Cards. &amp;#10;In the process of collecting JoyPoint, be careful of your opponent&amp;rsquo;s Trick Card because you&amp;rsquo;ll be surprised how it can drastically change the course of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use the Claw standee to get as many toys as possible and become the winner through these 3 simple actions:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Play a Trick Card (Optional)&amp;#10;     Move the Claw Standee and once it stops, take the Toy Card beneath it&amp;#10;     Claim a Dream Card by creating a set collection (according to its required condition)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when there is one pile that ran out of Toy Cards.&amp;#10;Players then count all their JoyPoints. The one with the highest JoyPoint is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Some people say: Be fast and you&amp;rsquo;ll get it! &amp;#10;But, is this true? Let&amp;rsquo;s Play!'&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
